******************************************** REDSHIFT **********************************************
Based on PostgreSQL, not used for OLTP (Online Transaction Processing) RDS is a good choice for OLTP
Redshift is good for OLAP Online analytical processing
10X better performance than other data warehouses, scale to PBs of data
 Columnar storage of data instead of row
 BI tools such as QuickSight or Tableau
 Redshift is not Multi AZ

****************************************** Athena & Quicksight ***************************
Athena:
     Serverless SQL quieries on top of data in S3
     Queries are logged in CloudTrail
     Good for sporadic queries
     Ready to use queries for VPC Flow Logs, CloudTrail, ALB Access logs, Cost and Usage reports etc.
Quicksight:
     BI tool for data visualization, creating dashboard
     Integrates with Athena, Redshift, EMS, RDS
